MEDICAL DISCLAIMER:

HemoScan is an AI-assisted tool designed to support healthcare professionals
in analyzing Complete Blood Count (CBC) reports. This software is intended for
informational and educational purposes only.

THIS SOFTWARE DOES NOT PROVIDE MEDICAL ADVICE. The information provided by
HemoScan should not be used for diagnosing or treating health problems or
diseases. Always seek the advice of qualified healthcare providers with any
questions you may have regarding a medical condition.

The developers and contributors of HemoScan are not responsible for any
decisions made based on the information provided by this software. Users
assume full responsibility for the use of this software and any consequences
thereof.

By using HemoScan, you acknowledge that:
1. This software is not a substitute for professional medical advice
2. You will consult qualified healthcare providers for medical decisions
